<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-12-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-12-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="362" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d362">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.001B14.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to
                                Ex-President <persName type="to">Ramón Báez</persName>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-12-08">
                                    <hi rend="italic">December 8, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>At the moment when you relinquish the executive power I desire to express
                            my great appreciation of your unselfish and patriotic conduct during a
                            most trying time and to convey to you my personal good wishes.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Woodrow Wilson</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>